{"tid":848731,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱既人，多數都係鑽左牛角尖","createTime":"2018-10-05T07:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T19:39:47.000Z","uid":123335,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"40897662d6858424492aae8d1107a1ee6f14249c","tid":848731,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"所謂「物極必反」<br />\n任何野 too much 都係 leads to bad ending <br />\nEg 飲水係健康，但飲水過量，都會中水毒<br />\n<br />\n而抑鬱既人<br />\n就係思想方面有某d 位 too much<br />\n放大得太緊要<br />\nEg 樣衰就覺得人生已完<br />\n生得矮就覺得人生已完<br />\n人際差就覺得人生已完<br />\n讀書差就覺得人生已完<br />\n有感情錯失就覺得人生已完<br />\n屋企背景差就覺得人生已完<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒<br />\n任何野Too much 永遠lead to bad end <br />\n睇開d 啦<br />\n人生無完美, 先係最完美"},{"pid":"d6f1208db160c464472c10e6ae5440ee749f463b","tid":848731,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"老實說，我人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279ef55e8ec3c1afb6ad9fd38deedc42d2c84320","tid":848731,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f1208db160c464472c10e6ae5440ee749f463b","tid":848731,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"老實說，我人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:18:04.000Z","msg":"點會呀<br />\n你仲有馬道克，六合彩燈神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddc92552d3c022f4e1a1dccd7dcde718bc700fb","tid":848731,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"279ef55e8ec3c1afb6ad9fd38deedc42d2c84320","tid":848731,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6f1208db160c464472c10e6ae5440ee749f463b","tid":848731,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"老實說，我人生已完<img src=\